# AI Assistant Workspace Rules & Deploy Guide

Please follow these guidelines automatically whenever making changes to this codebase:

---

## 1. Automated GitHub Pushes (For Vercel CDN Deploys)
* Whenever you modify files in `client-portal/`, `admin-portal/`, `marketing-site/`, or the backend `app/`, you **MUST** commit and push the changes to GitHub.
* Pushing to GitHub (branch `main` for `client-portal/`, branch `master` for root) automatically triggers Vite/Vercel CDN builds on Vercel (`client.buykori.app`, `admin.buykori.app`, `buykori.app`).

---

## 2. Client Portal Build & Local Static Sync
* If you edit any code in `client-portal/src/`, you **must** build the production bundle and copy it to the static fallback folder of the backend:
  1. Run `npm run build` inside `client-portal/`.
  2. Clear old assets: `Remove-Item -Recurse -Force "app\static\client-portal\assets\*"`
  3. Copy new build: `Copy-Item -Recurse -Force "client-portal\dist\*" "app\static\client-portal\"`

---

## 3. Server Deployments (DigitalOcean Droplet)
* To deploy python backend code and static fallback assets to the DigitalOcean Droplet, run:
  ```powershell
  python scratch/deploy_updates.py
  ```
  from the workspace root. This syncs changes, applies database migrations, and restarts the web/worker services.
